uk.gov.gchq.palisade.cache.service.request

Class CacheRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.gov.gchq.palisade.service.request.Request
      • uk.gov.gchq.palisade.cache.service.request.CacheRequest
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AddCacheRequest, GetCacheRequest, ListCacheRequest

    public abstract class CacheRequest
extends Request
    This is the basic cache request object. Each cache request is associated with a Service which is used to namespace the items in the cache. A key must also be provided which is used to look things up in the cache.

    All methods in this class throw NullPointerException if parameters are unset.
